metadata.name: Highly potent
metadata.description:
This is #1 of my ongoing series; "Kikker & Kubus".
-> Translated from Dutch: Frog and Cube

This series will be ongoing for as long as GY is here on earth because my devotion for frog art is never-ending. 

Discover GY's muse with this frog & cube themed 1/1 series. Every artwork is handmade on Procreate with the aid of mind altering substances, merged with an introspective glimpse of deeply rooted feelings that would have otherwise been cemented in my own consciousness.

Thank YOU for encouraging me to express myself.
